Lifts the tempo of a word or phrase. Use sparingly and only when appropriate.

```jsx
<div>
<h4 className="typography-body-10 text-muted mb-3">For example:</h4>
<p className="typography-body-10 mb-2 ml-4"><span className="text-success font-bold">Do:</span> Congratulations!</p>
<p className="typography-body-10 ml-4"><span className="text-danger font-bold">Don't:</span> Get in touch with us!</p>
</div>
```
